### Create C++ (g++)
POST https://localhost:7210/api/v1/runtimes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "runtimeName": "C++ (g++)",
  "runtimeVersion": "local",
  "defaultTimeLimitMs": 1000,
  "defaultMemoryLimitKb": 262144,
  "isActive": true
}

### Create C (gcc)
POST https://localhost:7210/api/v1/runtimes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "runtimeName": "C (gcc)",
  "runtimeVersion": "local",
